channel.title: New svn
channel.description:
Temporary SVN
http://opensvn.csie.org/hybridscape/ Same username and pass as before. If you don't know the pass PM me, mopar, silab, or fasga for it
[b][u]This is an SVN meaning before you do any major changes to the code you must update BEFORE YOU START CODING[/u][/b] Because SVN does not merge changes. It will overwrite any previous version of that file.
For SVN you must have TortoiseSVN. If you complain about having to download TortoiseCVS then SVN, don't. Everything normal person has both =/
We are now pending for SourceForge (Then we will have SVN, CVS, everything :P) INTSTRUCTIONS: Go to your hybridscape dir right click>SVN Checkout
